=ZE \ GOSUB 150290 FOR Y=WN TO NY \ FOR X=WN TO NXXL=X-WNXP=X+WNYL=Y-WNYP=Y+WN300 num=POINT(XL,YL)+POINT(X,YL)+POINT(XP,YL)+POINT(XL,Y)+POINT(
